POST        /register-to-vote/date-of-birth          controllers.step.DateOfBirthController.post
GET         /register-to-vote/edit/date-of-birth     controllers.step.DateOfBirthController.editGet
POST        /register-to-vote/edit/date-of-birth     controllers.step.DateOfBirthController.editPost
       
#Nino Step
